{"article_id":"PJov88S9b7Ghqn0J","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New York","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( CNN Business )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Facebook announced Thursday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that it had designated some high-profile people ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"including Nation of Islam leader Louis Farrakhan ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"who 's notorious for using anti-Semitic language ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"and right-wing conspiracy theorist Alex Jones ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"as `` dangerous ''","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"it will be purging them from its platforms .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Jones and his media outlet InfoWars had previously been banned fromin August 2018 ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"but had maintained a presence on Instagram ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"which is owned by Facebook .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"On Thursday , Jones and InfoWars will be barred from Instagram as well .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Other people","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"banned on Thursday","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"included Paul Nehlen , an anti-Semite","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"who unsuccessfully ran for Congress in 2016 and 2018 ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"and fringe right-wing media personalities Laura Loomer , Milo Yiannopoulos and Paul Joseph Watson .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"`` We 've always banned individuals or organizations","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that promote or engage in violence and hate ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"regardless of ideology , ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"a Facebook spokesperson said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"provided to CNN Business .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"`` The process","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"for evaluating potential violators","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"is extensive","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and it is what led us to our decision","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to remove these accounts today . ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"A Facebook spokesperson told CNN Business","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the company goes through a lengthy process","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and takes into consideration a number of factors","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"before determining an individual to be `` dangerous . ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"The Facebook spokesperson said","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"such factors include whether the person or organization has ever called for violence against individuals","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"based on race , ethnicity , or national origin ;","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"whether the person has been identified with a hateful ideology ;","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"whether they use hate speech or slurs in their about section on their social media profiles ;","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and whether they have had pages or groups removed from Facebook","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"for violating hate speech rules .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"In some instances ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"when Facebook bans an individual or organization ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"it also restricts others from expressing praise or support for them on its platforms ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"the spokesperson said ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that the company continues to view such action as the correct approach .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"That policy may not apply to any or all of the people","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"banned Thursday , however .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"The spokesperson added","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that Facebook will remove groups , pages and accounts","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"created","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to represent the banned individuals","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"when it knows","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the individual is participating in the effort .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Some of the individuals","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"who were designated as `` dangerous ''","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"responded to the ban on their accounts in the brief period between when Facebook announced the ban and when Facebook scrubbed the accounts .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Loomer , for instance , denied in an Instagram post","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that she ever violated the company 's terms of service .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Loomer asked people to follow her on an different platform ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` Looks like you guys will probably never hear from me again . ''","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Watson used Twitter ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"from which he has not been banned ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to write ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"`` In an authoritarian society","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"controlled by a handful of Silicon Valley giants ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"all dissent must be purged . ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Farrakhan , Jones and Nehlen did not immediately respond to requests for comment .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"Some critics questioned","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"why Facebook banned the accounts in one fell swoop on Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"instead of taking action against the accounts at the time","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"they were determined to have been in violation of the company 's rules .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"These critics suggested","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the announcement was designed","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"to generate positive publicity for the company ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"which has a history","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"of being slow to act on such matters","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"and of only taking action","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"after facing pressure from the public .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"It is possible it simply took Facebook a significant amount of time","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"to reach a decision","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"on whether to label the individuals as `` dangerous . ''","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"In late March , Business Insider obtained emails","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"showing Facebook executives in an intense debate","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"over whether or not to take action like this against Jones .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"At the time , a Facebook spokesperson told CNN Business ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"`` As this email correspondence shows ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"we continually monitor and review","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"whether people are involved in organized hate on our platform .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"We 've already taken down InfoWars ' Facebook Page ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"but Alex Jones has a network of presences online","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"and we are evaluating how to appropriately enforce our policies against him as an individual .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"We 're committed to being diligent","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and will share an update","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"when that process has run its course . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":191,"left":0,"right":190,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":113,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":1,"right":112,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":112,"left":107,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":103,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":2,"right":102,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":8,"right":9,"relation"